818
00:48:15.800 --> 00:48:17.960
Poor people and ugly people.

819
00:48:18.840 --> 00:48:20.000
I know.

820
00:48:20.080 --> 00:48:22.480
My sister is a right-wing disabled person.

821
00:48:36.040 --> 00:48:37.680
You see.

822
