824
00:48:45.120 --> 00:48:49.880
And when she sees ugly people.
she sees ugly people. That's just it.

825
00:48:49.960 --> 00:48:51.920
I wish I had a better rationale.

826
00:48:52.000 --> 00:48:54.440
As you can imagine.

