00:49:03.840 --> 00:49:06.560
I wouldn't be here
telling you about my own shit

831
00:49:06.640 --> 00:49:08.360
and being paid for it

832
00:49:08.440 --> 00:49:09.560
if it wasn't for her.

833
00:49:09.640 --> 00:49:11.160
I would have grown up

834
