This is who I'd be.

841
00:49:31.320 --> 00:49:32.480
This person.

842
00:49:33.880 --> 00:49:34.720
And…

843
00:49:36.000 --> 00:49:37.640
I owe my sister everything.

844
00:49:37.720 --> 00:49:39.360
But you see.

845
00:49:39.440 --> 00:49:42.120
growing up with her wasn't easy.

846
00:49:42.200 --> 00:49:45.480
When she wanted to ask someone.
"What do you do?" at a party.

847
00:49:45.560 --> 00:49:48.160
her anxiety turned her question
into something like…

848
00:49:50.800 --> 00:49:51.640
"You."

849
00:49:53.040 --> 00:49:53.880
"You."

850
00:49:56.400 --> 00:49:57.520
"What do you do?"

851
00:49:58.720 --> 00:50:01.320
"I'm unemployed at the moment."

852
