00:50:10.520 --> 00:50:12.640
In true Goldoni-style.

856
00:50:14.240 --> 00:50:15.640
Very 18th-century theater.

857
00:50:18.360 --> 00:50:19.200
I was…

858
00:50:19.960 --> 00:50:21.840
