what disability was.

950
00:56:18.080 --> 00:56:21.160
The only disabled people they knew
were those in a wheelchair.

951
00:56:21.240 --> 00:56:24.280
If you didn't have that.
they'd question you.

952
00:56:24.360 --> 00:56:27.520
People wouldn't come up
and ask me things like.

953
00:56:27.600 --> 00:56:31.360
"Michela. you're incredibly beautiful.
What's your secret?"

954
00:56:31.440 --> 00:56:34.200
No. they would look at me
and go like this…

955
00:56:38.560 --> 00:56:39.800
"Your sister.

956
00:56:41.280 --> 00:56:42.440
what's wrong with her?"

957
00:56:44.880 --> 00:56:46.000
"Does she have it?"

958
00:56:47.320 --> 00:56:49.400
"The disabled parking permit?"

959
00:56:50.800 --> 00:56:52.680
"No. my sister can walk."

960
00:56:52.760 --> 00:56:54.280
"How come?"

961
00:56:54.360 --> 00:56:57.760
"If you have the disabled badge.
you're part of a caste."

962
00:56:58.480 --> 00:57:00.480
"You can park in the center of Rome."

963
00:57:00.560 --> 00:57:03.240
"You can get the best seats
at the Olimpico for the derby."

