969
00:57:19.520 --> 00:57:21.440
let alone for those like your sister."

970
00:57:22.120 --> 00:57:24.320
"Is it always Black Friday for you?"

971
00:57:26.600 --> 00:57:28.280
"Do you get free cinema tickets?"

972
00:57:28.360 --> 00:57:31.440
"Not that your sister understands movies."

973
00:57:31.520 --> 00:57:34.040
"No. it doesn't work like that."

974
00:57:34.560 --> 00:57:38.480
"What's wrong with her?
Is she differently-abled?

975
00:57:38.560 --> 00:57:41.920
"I mean. otherwise.
she wouldn't be like this."

976
00:57:42.000 --> 00:57:45.400
"What's wrong with her?
Has she got Down's?"

977
00:57:45.480 --> 00:57:47.400
"Is she more up or more down?"

978
00:57:47.480 --> 00:57:49.600
"Sorry. I was trying to lighten the mood."

979
00:57:53.160 --> 00:57:55.440
"What is she. spastic?"

980
00:57:55.520 --> 00:57:56.360
"No."

981
00:57:56.440 --> 00:57:58.640
-"Is she Bamboleiro?"
-"What's Bamboleiro?"

982
00:57:58.720 --> 00:57:59.760
"Yes. Bamboleiro!"

983
00:57:59.840 --> 00:58:02.640
"Like those people who walk funny.
with mangled legs."

984
00:58:02.720 --> 00:58:04.120
